    "excerpt": "A prayer written for the people of Washington DC during the Trump administration's authoritarian push, August 2025.  . . .",
    "content": "<div class=\"english\" lang=\"eng-Latn\" style=\"font-size: 1.2em;\">\nA prayer written for the people of Washington DC during the Trump administration&#8217;s authoritarian push, August 2025.\n</div>\n<hr />\n<table style=\"margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto;\" class=\"draggable toggleable-table\">\n<thead>\n<tr>\n<th id=\"x\" style=\"text-align: right;\"><a href=\"/translate/\" target=\"_blank\">Contribute&nbsp;a&nbsp;translation</a></th>\n<th style=\"text-align: left;\">Source (English)</th>\n</tr>\n</thead>\n<tbody>\n<tr>\n<td style=\"vertical-align:top;\">\n<div class=\"liturgy\" lang=\"heb-Hebr\" style=\"text-align: right;\">\n</div>\n</td>\n<td style=\"vertical-align:top;\">\n<div class=\"english\" lang=\"eng-Latn\" style=\"text-align: left;\">\n<span class=\"divine-referent\">God</span>,<br />\nplease be with the people<br />\nof Washington DC.\n</div>\n</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td style=\"vertical-align:top;\">\n<div class=\"liturgy\" lang=\"heb-Hebr\" style=\"text-align: right;\">\n</div>\n</td>\n<td style=\"vertical-align:top;\">\n<div class=\"english\" lang=\"eng-Latn\" style=\"text-align: left;\">\nProtect the most vulnerable,<br />\ngive them the shelter of your peace.<br />\nRemind them<br />\nthat they are not alone,<br />\nthat we are with them.\n</div>\n</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td style=\"vertical-align:top;\">\n<div class=\"liturgy\" lang=\"heb-Hebr\" style=\"text-align: right;\">\n</div>\n</td>\n<td style=\"vertical-align:top;\">\n<div class=\"english\" lang=\"eng-Latn\" style=\"text-align: left;\">\nBring us a world<br />\nof everlasting love<br />\nand togetherness.<br />\nA world free<br />\nfrom authoritarianism,<br />\nwhere there are no police,<br />\nno weapons,<br />\nno jails,<br />\nno borders,<br />\nno hatred.\n</div>\n</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td style=\"vertical-align:top;\">\n<div class=\"liturgy\" lang=\"heb-Hebr\" style=\"text-align: right;\">\n</div>\n</td>\n<td style=\"vertical-align:top;\">\n<div class=\"english\" lang=\"eng-Latn\" style=\"text-align: left;\">\nMake this prayer<br />\nlike a pebble in water,<br />\na ripple of holiness<br />\nthat reaches<br />\nacross this moment,<br />\nacross this table,<br />\nthis home,<br />\nthis city,<br />\nand this world.\n</div>\n</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td style=\"vertical-align:top;\">\n<div class=\"liturgy\" lang=\"heb-Hebr\" style=\"text-align: right;\">\n</div>\n</td>\n<td style=\"vertical-align:top;\">\n<div class=\"english\" lang=\"eng-Latn\" style=\"text-align: left;\">\nHear us,<br />\nso that we may heal our brokenness<br />\nseven generations back<br />\nand seven generations forward.<br />\n<em>Amen</em>.\n </div>\n</td>\n</tr>\n</tbody>\n</table>\n<hr />\n<p>This prayer, by Madeline Peltz, was offered after the issuance of the Executive Order entitled &#8220;<a href=\"https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Declaring_a_Crime_Emergency_in_the_District_of_Columbia\">Declaring a Crime Emergency in the District of Columbia</a>&#8221; on 11 August 2025.</p>\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n",
